snippet.title: Vesica Institute
snippet.description:
The Vesica Institute for Holistic Studies founded by Dr. Robert J. Gilbert.

Dr. Gilbert has a multi-faceted background in both spiritual and scientific studies and has studied multiple world spiritual traditions extensively, with advanced information from key systems integrated into the Vesica trainings. 

SPIRITUAL SCIENCE
VIBRATIONAL SCIENCE
BIOGEOMETRY ENERGY BALANCING
HEALING TECHNOLOGY OF STONES & CRYSTALS

- Live & Online Courses -
